{"title":"a-b问题","uid":"c104b3cf721ac819bf3e3a3017d84c96","slug":"a-b问题-1","date":"2023-07-31T11:12:21.000Z","updated":"2023-07-31T11:15:23.128Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/a-b问题-1.json","keywords":"serverDream's blog","cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"A-B问题\"><a href=\"#A-B问题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"A - B问题\"></a>A - B问题</h1><h2 id=\"题目背景\"><a href=\"#题目背景\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题目背景\"></a>题目背景</h2><p>小明他是个大聪明，他只会加法，不会减法(总也比小A他家计算器牛)，请你帮TA写一个程序，辅助他学会减法。</p>\n<h2 id=\"题目描述\"><a href=\"#题目描述\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题目描述\"></a>题目描述</h2><p>小明给你了a和b帮他算出a+b等于几。</p>\n<h2 id=\"输入格式\"><a href=\"#输入格式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"输入格式\"></a>输入格式</h2><p>两个整数a和b。</p>\n<h2 id=\"输出格式\"><a href=\"#输出格式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"输出格式\"></a>输出格式</h2><p>请你帮TA算出a+b的结果。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;iostream></span>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">//导入输入输出头文件</span></span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">using</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">namespace</span> std<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"token function\">main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> a<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> b<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">//定义变量a和b</span>\n    cin <span class=\"token operator\">>></span> a <span class=\"token operator\">>></span> b<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">//输入a与b</span>\n    cout <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> b <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span> endl<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">//输出a-b的结果</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n\n\n","text":"A - B问题题目背景小明他是个大聪明，他只会加法，不会减法(总也比小A他家计算器牛)，请你帮TA写一个程序，辅助他学会减法。 题目描述小明给你了a和b帮他算出a+b等于几。 输入格式两个整数a和b。 输出格式请你帮TA算出a+b的结果。 #include &lt;iostrea...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":342,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"C++基础","slug":"C-基础","count":3,"path":"api/tags/C-基础.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#A-B%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\"><span class=\"toc-text\">A - B问题</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%AE%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF\"><span class=\"toc-text\">题目背景</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%AE%E6%8F%8F%E8%BF%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">题目描述</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">输入格式</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">输出格式</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"serverDream","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/140633744?v=4","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"变量","uid":"66ac6fe79dbb9aa78f5e1cf305b49e4a","sl